=== Pronunciation ===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
כּנּרת   - כּנּרות / kinnerôth  kinnereth / kin-ner-oth', kin-neh'-reth
=== Etymology ===

Respectively plural and singular feminine from the same as [[כּנּור]] {{HH|3658}}; perhaps harp shaped; 
=== Proper noun ===
[[Kinneroth]] or [[Kinnereth]], a place in Palestine: - Chinnereth, Chinneroth, Cinneroth.